1
00:00:06,520 --> 00:00:09,930
[A Mission of the Heart]

2
00:00:09,950 --> 00:00:10,940
[Episode 8]

3
00:00:10,990 --> 00:00:14,280
[Xiafeng House]

4
00:00:59,100 --> 00:01:00,350
Tell me,

5
00:01:01,290 --> 00:01:03,200
should I compete for Yu?

6
00:01:11,140 --> 00:01:11,870
So annoying!

7
00:01:15,800 --> 00:01:16,800
What do you think?

8
00:01:29,180 --> 00:01:30,710
This is exactly the flavor.

9
00:01:31,850 --> 00:01:32,780
Now,

10
00:01:32,800 --> 00:01:35,039
it's my time to enjoy tasty food.

11
00:01:35,330 --> 00:01:36,700
I don't want to see anyone,

12
00:01:36,700 --> 00:01:38,380
especially Lu Sanliang.

13
00:01:46,720 --> 00:01:48,479
If you don't want to see me,

14
00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:50,120
who do you want to see?

15
00:01:51,030 --> 00:01:51,800
My Lord...

16
00:01:52,280 --> 00:01:53,789
did you come to me...

17
00:01:53,820 --> 00:01:56,280
because there's something you need
from me?

18
00:02:13,570 --> 00:02:14,830
Go perform an autopsy.

19
00:02:17,600 --> 00:02:18,070
Well,

20
00:02:19,329 --> 00:02:20,810
what's wrong with him?

21
00:02:20,970 --> 00:02:22,930
Performing an autopsy
in the middle of the night again—

22
00:02:22,930 --> 00:02:23,810
so annoying.

23
00:02:25,100 --> 00:02:27,390
My clothes stink. Seriously.

24
00:02:41,190 --> 00:02:42,600
Having a superior like Lu Sanliang

25
00:02:42,600 --> 00:02:44,770
who makes people work at night every day

26
00:02:44,770 --> 00:02:46,250
is truly unbearable.

27
00:03:07,430 --> 00:03:09,580
Who is this man in black?

28
00:03:10,250 --> 00:03:11,740
What is he looking for?

29
00:03:12,390 --> 00:03:14,650
Could it be related to Chen Zhao's death?

30
00:03:15,740 --> 00:03:17,470
It's not with Chen Zhao either.

31
00:03:17,620 --> 00:03:19,150
Where on earth is it?

32
00:04:07,640 --> 00:04:09,900
I didn't expect this drug to be so potent.

33
00:04:28,820 --> 00:04:29,770
So?

34
00:04:30,900 --> 00:04:32,300
It's the Threads of Love.

35
00:04:33,140 --> 00:04:34,270
The Threads of Love?

36
00:04:34,440 --> 00:04:36,440
It sounds like an aphrodisiac,

37
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:37,590
but actually,

38
00:04:37,610 --> 00:04:38,880
it's a deadly poison.

39
00:04:38,980 --> 00:04:40,780
Once it's mixed into wine or water,

40
00:04:40,780 --> 00:04:43,380
it'll be very difficult
to detect traces of it.

41
00:04:50,760 --> 00:04:51,380
Let's go.

42
00:05:00,620 --> 00:05:02,220
If someone is poisoned by it,

43
00:05:02,770 --> 00:05:03,860
what are the symptoms?

44
00:05:03,860 --> 00:05:05,090
The person poisoned by it

45
00:05:05,090 --> 00:05:06,820
will very likely die suddenly.

46
00:05:07,430 --> 00:05:09,350
The symptoms are a bit like fatal syncope
during intercourse.

47
00:05:09,350 --> 00:05:12,080
That's why I failed
to detect it in time back then.

48
00:05:17,870 --> 00:05:18,600
My Lord,

49
00:05:18,860 --> 00:05:21,120
don't tell me
for the sake of the case investigation,

50
00:05:21,120 --> 00:05:22,200
you ate that...

51
00:05:22,370 --> 00:05:24,090
you ate that aphrodisiac.

52
00:05:25,520 --> 00:05:27,840
Just a little bit. It won't kill me.

53
00:05:31,610 --> 00:05:33,080
Is there an antidote?

54
00:05:33,440 --> 00:05:36,370
I'll have Commander Li
prepare the antidote for you.

55
00:05:40,400 --> 00:05:42,200
Why go through all that trouble?

56
00:05:51,970 --> 00:05:52,900
My Lord,

57
00:05:53,659 --> 00:05:54,730
could it be...

58
00:05:55,490 --> 00:05:57,550
you already have someone you love?

59
00:06:13,110 --> 00:06:14,230
From now on,

60
00:06:14,760 --> 00:06:16,690
don't mention anyone irrelevant.

61
00:06:17,850 --> 00:06:18,710
Do you hear me?

62
00:06:49,620 --> 00:06:52,210
Honey. I think we should give up today.

63
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:54,570
I don't think
our son is coming back tonight.

64
00:06:54,570 --> 00:06:56,200
It's all your fault.

65
00:06:56,310 --> 00:06:58,730
You insisted
on him joining the Imperial Guard.

66
00:06:58,730 --> 00:07:00,410
Now he's as cold-faced as Yama.

67
00:07:00,410 --> 00:07:02,670
Everyone keeps their distance from him.

68
00:07:02,770 --> 00:07:04,030
This time, no matter what,

69
00:07:04,030 --> 00:07:05,220
we must catch this brat

70
00:07:05,220 --> 00:07:07,220
and make him go back for blind dates.

71
00:07:11,490 --> 00:07:12,490
Hurry! Hurry!

72
00:07:12,830 --> 00:07:14,540
My Lord, we've arrived.

73
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:17,220
Officer Huang,
please take him back to the mansion.

74
00:07:17,220 --> 00:07:19,080
I'll go prepare the antidote now.

75
00:07:19,350 --> 00:07:20,090
Be careful!

76
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:29,800
Mrs. Lu, Mr. Lu,

77
00:07:30,310 --> 00:07:32,070
what are you... doing here?

78
00:07:32,130 --> 00:07:32,860
Zhao,

79
00:07:32,890 --> 00:07:34,420
the girl who carried Zhan inside just now—

80
00:07:34,420 --> 00:07:35,850
who is she?

81
00:07:37,300 --> 00:07:38,370
She's Officer Huang Yu,

82
00:07:38,370 --> 00:07:39,510
a new member of the Imperial Guard

83
00:07:39,510 --> 00:07:41,040
recruited by Lord Lu.

84
00:07:41,060 --> 00:07:42,990
She is Huang Yu?

85
00:07:43,240 --> 00:07:44,560
Honey. Honey.

86
00:07:44,710 --> 00:07:46,860
She's the girl who saved me last time.

87
00:07:47,020 --> 00:07:48,800
Our son can be saved!

88
00:07:50,550 --> 00:07:52,080
What happened to Zhan?

89
00:07:52,290 --> 00:07:54,440
Why did he need a girl
to carry him inside?

90
00:07:54,440 --> 00:07:56,200
When Lord Lu was working on the case,

91
00:07:56,200 --> 00:07:56,990
he accidentally took an aphrodisiac.

92
00:07:56,990 --> 00:07:57,690
But don't worry.

93
00:07:57,690 --> 00:07:59,700
I'll go prepare the antidote right away.

94
00:07:59,700 --> 00:08:01,990
If... he doesn't take the antidote,

95
00:08:02,020 --> 00:08:03,480
will his life be in danger?

96
00:08:03,780 --> 00:08:04,780
No.

97
00:08:04,810 --> 00:08:07,670
It's just that...
Lord Lu will feel uncomfortable.

98
00:08:07,880 --> 00:08:09,810
Then there's no need to prepare it.

99
00:08:10,850 --> 00:08:11,320
Honey,

100
00:08:11,890 --> 00:08:14,210
I think there's no need
to punish our son like this.

101
00:08:14,210 --> 00:08:15,650
You don't understand.

102
00:08:15,930 --> 00:08:17,230
If we don't take this chance

103
00:08:17,230 --> 00:08:19,370
to let Yu and Zhan
spend quality time together,

104
00:08:19,370 --> 00:08:20,870
with that blockhead son of ours...

105
00:08:20,870 --> 00:08:21,660
Blockhead son?

106
00:08:21,660 --> 00:08:23,380
When can he ever get a wife?

107
00:08:24,270 --> 00:08:25,300
I think Yu

108
00:08:25,320 --> 00:08:27,320
is quite good to Zhan.

109
00:08:27,770 --> 00:08:29,450
Perhaps in the near future,

110
00:08:29,500 --> 00:08:31,740
we can become in-laws.

111
00:08:32,240 --> 00:08:33,549
Zhao, don't you agree?

112
00:08:33,570 --> 00:08:34,530
Yes, yes, yes.

113
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:37,080
Then tell us more

114
00:08:37,110 --> 00:08:39,370
about what happened between Yu and Zhan.

115
00:08:40,890 --> 00:08:41,919
Now?

116
00:08:42,120 --> 00:08:44,490
No, no, no.
It's not convenient to talk here.

117
00:08:44,490 --> 00:08:47,550
Come back to our mansion with us
and tell us all about it.

118
00:08:47,700 --> 00:08:49,370
Mrs. Lu, I don't think that's appropriate.

119
00:08:49,370 --> 00:08:50,660
-Oh, come on.
-Come on.

120
00:08:50,690 --> 00:08:51,400
No, no, no.

121
00:08:52,610 --> 00:08:53,070
My Lord,

122
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:55,160
I took off your clothes
because I was worried

123
00:08:55,160 --> 00:08:57,060
wearing them would make you
feel uncomfortable.

124
00:08:57,060 --> 00:08:59,390
I absolutely had no improper intentions.

125
00:09:00,290 --> 00:09:01,090
Is that so?

126
00:09:02,810 --> 00:09:03,770
I swear to God.

127
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:06,870
I think Commander Li

128
00:09:06,890 --> 00:09:08,510
should make the antidote ready soon.

129
00:09:08,510 --> 00:09:10,120
How about this?
I'll stand guard at the door.

130
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:11,720
Call me if you need anything.

131
00:09:21,950 --> 00:09:23,460
Huang Yu, you're so useless.

132
00:09:23,460 --> 00:09:25,630
How can you be so flustered?

133
00:09:27,880 --> 00:09:28,630
But

134
00:09:28,830 --> 00:09:29,900
the aphrodisiac

135
00:09:29,920 --> 00:09:31,620
is really potent.

136
00:09:31,710 --> 00:09:34,620
It has actually made Lu Zhan,
who's usually aloof and abstinent,

137
00:09:34,620 --> 00:09:36,300
become like this.
